    public abstract class EEFWidgetStyleImpl
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.impl.MinimalEObjectImpl.Container
implements EEFWidgetStyle
    An implementation of the model object 'EEF Widget Style'.

    The following features are implemented:

    • Label Background Color Expression
    • Label Foreground Color Expression
    • Label Font Name Expression
    • Label Font Size Expression
    • Label Font Style Expression
